{"tid":23922,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"轉工問題","createTime":"2016-12-05T08:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T06:28:18.000Z","uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"511aa79c59b785c96e2b487153d81e23de179cab","tid":23922,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:49:02.000Z","msg":"究竟每半年轉一次工有咩問題呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日同同事傾起呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢一句飛埋黎就話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉得咁密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條友一定有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實請問各位有咩問題呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da42eb632714e998fac1ac1ab990af3aa19338fa","tid":23922,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:50:04.000Z","msg":"做到頂唔順咪轉囉"},{"pid":"e3f1b6016ddc6001dda2b1948f880d22947dc5fd","tid":23922,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:50:22.000Z","msg":"正經post冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5164a5cf95ee14538174c244a7aee59b2f92cabb","tid":23922,"uid":43551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:50:56.000Z","msg":"有人請咪得，理得你幾耐轉"},{"pid":"1254104119aa81b58cb5d3c33f8702d188336d55","tid":23922,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:51:11.000Z","msg":"轉工可以有好多原因，唔可以一概而論，最緊要忠於自己，開開心心就得"},{"pid":"8d5e5938489951efd7aeea772344b29b557b301d","tid":23922,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做到頂唔順咪轉囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我隔黎個同事講到洪水猛獸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔知佢想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec78fcc45c7292c99f8d43ef643f0e5e5173781","tid":23922,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉工可以有好多原因，唔可以一概而論，最緊要忠於自己，開開心心就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公司班廢老個腦真係好難理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287696c74236b2d8f7d74fb6cd64e3443da45c71","tid":23922,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人請咪得，理得你幾耐轉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但今日個廢老就係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔肯請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話佢做唔長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我頂得好辛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e6a7a26f182d8c395bc7d5e5ae9ea8d76e6bdf","tid":23922,"uid":43551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有人請咪得，理得你幾耐轉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但今日個廢老就係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔肯請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話佢做唔長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我頂得好辛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽唔明你講乜"},{"pid":"47f69841e5017fa4b06e00d691cdbf6f423cdf89","tid":23922,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:16:59.000Z","msg":"你係老闆，請個人返黎培訓三個月，再多三個月就走，你會唔會請？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54a49baebfb36331d3c2d39f876472184ead980","tid":23922,"uid":19010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有人請咪得，理得你幾耐轉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但今日個廢老就係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔肯請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話佢做唔長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我頂得好辛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽唔明你講乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =廢老<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：聽講今日有新同事見工喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係呀！不過條友半年就轉一次工，我一定唔會請囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你負責見？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係呀！屌！正一垃圾90後！份份工做唔長！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：難得有人見都唔請？點解呀？<br />\n        （做撚死我咩，我已經一個人做3個人野）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：而家d後生真係冇用，成日轉工姐係代表本身能力有問題，又唔捱得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：（唔請人都咁多藉口，屌你老尾）嗯咁你後生一定好捱得啦，一個打十個，你好叻豬呀！大師兄"},{"pid":"0eeffe8bad40c9d61a9d8bb048902ac98525b436","tid":23922,"uid":32370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:35:09.000Z","msg":"份工好的話，有邊個想quit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac1abf2e2eb9d9229d9edd66fe5c6a16a7123ec","tid":23922,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係老闆，請個人返黎培訓三個月，再多三個月就走，你會唔會請？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個係其中一個好重要既原因( 請人個條友睇)<br />\n除非個位本身流動性就好大<br />\n好似SALES 之類<br />\n<br />\n再者 除非你理由好合理 <br />\n如公司執笠,公司由九龍灣轉去上水咁。<br />\n人地都會先入為主去覺得係你處理唔到人際關係/能力不足/揀工做之類<br />\n但就算你理由好合理,但百9幾份CV 得鬼閒睇到咁詳細<br />\n都係&quot;立&quot;下架啦<br />\n<br />\n所以如果個POST 係要穩定既人選,你好容易比人西走左"},{"pid":"568ba2cb6fc33c9e83ecafc1ca87487d6e21c783","tid":23922,"uid":43551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:37:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有人請咪得，理得你幾耐轉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但今日個廢老就係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔肯請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話佢做唔長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我頂得好辛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽唔明你講乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =廢老<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：聽講今日有新同事見工喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係呀！不過條友半年就轉一次工，我一定唔會請囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你負責見？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係呀！屌！正一垃圾90後！份份工做唔長！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：難得有人見都唔請？點解呀？<br />\n        （做撚死我咩，我已經一個人做3個人野）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：而家d後生真係冇用，成日轉工姐係代表本身能力有問題，又唔捱得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：（唔請人都咁多藉口，屌你老尾）嗯咁你後生一定好捱得啦，一個打十個，你好叻豬呀！大師兄</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁佢係唔想請人，關幾耐咩事"},{"pid":"bcbdbde39e77a5bc20516d64cae2d8677fa03e1e","tid":23922,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係老闆，請個人返黎培訓三個月，再多三個月就走，你會唔會請？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個係其中一個好重要既原因( 請人個條友睇)<br />\n除非個位本身流動性就好大<br />\n好似SALES 之類<br />\n<br />\n再者 除非你理由好合理 <br />\n如公司執笠,