ote><br />\nSO FAR..我轉左3次工<br />\n都係年半左右走<br />\n有一次試用期內一個月就走<br />\n小文員一名..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉工加人工係咪真係加到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1.9500<br />\n2.12500<br />\n3.16000<br />\n<br />\n睇運氣..唔好做標準..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個升覆都好吸引喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲係13k 文員仔咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807f7be385f3b5d009d303bee6a37ecff79b466a","tid":23922,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:19:31.000Z","msg":"一兩份正常 經常性就有問題"},{"pid":"e2997016bbb7041469a0a67e5d45294ca4bdf033","tid":23922,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:24:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係老闆，請個人返黎培訓三個月，再多三個月就走，你會唔會請？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個係其中一個好重要既原因( 請人個條友睇)<br />\n除非個位本身流動性就好大<br />\n好似SALES 之類<br />\n<br />\n再者 除非你理由好合理 <br />\n如公司執笠,公司由九龍灣轉去上水咁。<br />\n人地都會先入為主去覺得係你處理唔到人際關係/能力不足/揀工做之類<br />\n但就算你理由好合理,但百9幾份CV 得鬼閒睇到咁詳細<br />\n都係&quot;立&quot;下架啦<br />\n<br />\n所以如果個POST 係要穩定既人選,你好容易比人西走左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果做得辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁應該做幾耐先好轉工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊次次都係做幾個月唔做<br />\n份份工都咁辛苦就算鳩數啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得 你3個月內一定知份工大概有幾辛苦,<br />\n如果有旺淡季,你都預計到 旺季實做到仆街..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港19公司數量太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三個月試用走其實我覺得好正路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係大家試大家適唔適合咁姐<br />\n但奈何真係唔適合，都要捱一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實幾慘<br />\n人生有幾多個一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" clas